HEADWORD: Nothingness
<hw>Noth"ing*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Nihility;
nonexistence.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being of no value; a thing of no
value.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nothings</ent>⟦br⟧
